The entire dataset can be automatically downloaded and loaded into your local session. We have included a cell in our notebook that automatically downloads the SST-2 and QNLI dataset. 

The datasets can be found on the HuggingFace website. 

[SST-2]{https://huggingface.co/datasets/stanfordnlp/sst2/tree/main}
[QNLI]{https://huggingface.co/datasets/SetFit/qnli}
